%^BOLD%^-=%^WHITE%^Glory Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Representing the glory of a righteous cause, you bring light and justice to the darkness and depravity of the world.

Clerics with the Glory Domain gain the following benefits:
- Immunity to fear effects.

The Glory domain contains the following spells:

Searing Light, Haste, Archon Aura, Righteous Might, Greater Heroism

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Jarmila, Edea

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
